import {MdOutlineLibraryMusic, MdOutlineCategory} from 'react-icons/md'

import {PiMusicNotesPlus} from 'react-icons/pi'
import {AiOutlineStar} from 'react-icons/ai'
import {BsArrowLeft,BsArrowRight} from 'react-icons/bs'

const icons = {
    MdOutlineLibraryMusic,
    RiDonutChartLine,
    FcLineChart,
    PiMusicNotesPlus,
    MdOutlineCategory,
    AiOutlineStar,
    BsArrowLeft,
    BsArrowRight,
    BiSearch
}

export default icons
